            When marketing and selling to Russian- and Serbian-speaking
            audiences, it is crucial to present campaigns in a language the
            audiences understand. If your marketing materials are in a different
            language, marketing translation becomes essential. However, it’s not
            enough to translate accurately—your marketing must also be
            culturally adapted. As you can imagine, implementing marketing
            translation is a long and complicated process.
        </p>

